Requires libsqlite3.

On Ubuntu/Debian:
    sudo apt install libsqlite3

    sudo apt install libsqlite3-dev (?)

=================

Random tidbits:

Alt + click drags the whole window (Linux Mint)
    System settings - Windows - Behaviour - Special key to move and resize windows

=================

Create distribution packages (best practice):

.deb for Debian/Ubuntu: declare libsqlite3-0 as a dependency.
.rpm for Fedora/RHEL: declare sqlite-libs as dependency.
.AppImage for portable Linux: bundle everything in one file.
Snap/Flatpak: handle dependencies in manifest.
